data.description: If space is what you are needing, look no further!  This home features 4 bedrooms plus 3 living areas, formal(set up as theater room) informal with gas fireplace, sun room fully heated and cooled. Plantation shutters cover all windows for privacy and all windows have darkening screens.  Just over one year old fridge in kitchen to stay, approximately 1 year old dishwasher also.  Water heater 2017. Located close to Weeks golf course, 10-15 minutes to Sheppard AFB.  Fain Elementary and new Legacy HS zoned.
